Class AddTagDialogController

java.lang.Object
view.AddTagDialogController
public class AddTagDialogController extends Object
Controller for the Add Tag Dialog. This class handles the logic for adding a tag to a photo, including selecting a tag type and entering a tag value.
Author:
Reuben Thomas, Ryan Zaken
